<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>So what if the RTA suddenly decides to put AD, Grummus, and Behemoth on rotation? You'll just suddenly stop teaming? LOL. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
