<br>
You see folks Shogon is right there is a linear progression to this game... and lots of us haven't done that.  Never killed a NToV dragon (and no Eashen and Iki don't count), never killed a Ssra boss, never seen VT, never killed AoW.  So you want to skip this content and go straight for the phat l377s in PoP?  Not likely.  I would imagine going into the planes with our Incarnadine BP, our wars at 6.5K hps fully buffed, our clerics with smaller mana pools will get us all killed quick.  With the equipment upgrades offered in NToV, Ssra, and VT our guilds can take the beating from the mobs in the elemental planes... but not yet.  AA's will never overcome the equipment upgrades to be had in these zones... NEVER.<br>
<br>
Frankly what's done is done and grats to you guys on getting flagged for HoH.  I agree with the powers that be that no two guilds should team up for a flagging mob.  It sets a precedent that could indeed cause some serious problems on this server in the future.<br>
