  Let's start out by saying that my opinions are mine, and not my guilds.<br>
<br>
  AD was a blast, my heart was racing the whole time, and I kept thinking... &quot;We are so, so, so gonna die.&quot; But you know what? We didn't. We did an amazing job. We killed AD with no primals, no vex thal gear, and a good deal of us missing spells that cost 50k. The guild leaders from VoLS and CB spent alot of time and effort coordinating everything, and ya know what? We kicked some serious ass. 72 people got flags, and we were proud of ourselves. <br>
<br>
 Whatever happend to congratufuckinglations? You take our accomplisment and turn it into something over-blown and make us look like we run around breaking rules left and right. It's been said 500 times, AD is not a rot mob, and so we didn't break the no teaming for rot mob rule. We had maybe 4 or 5 people over the 72 people raid limit, and half of us went ld on the pull, so screw us, damn zergers, we should be banned!<br>
<br>
  I think everyone is starting to see through all the bs, to what this is really about. The top tier pulling the strings, and not wanting to share. Who the hell are you, or anyone else to tell us how to progress through EQ? We'll make our own way through things, how we see fit. &quot;You can't go to so and so zone, if you haven't farmed these items for this many people.&quot; Whatever, the game's versatile, there are usually more than a single way to do things.<br>
<br>
  The funny thing is, since getting our flags, I haven't seen anyone from VoLS in HOH hardly at all. I think that most of us noob guilds are fed up with you telling us what to do, that we amount to nothing, that we zerg, and train, and stink up your space. Just go ahead and keep bending the rules to better suit your needs. But be careful, one day you are gonna push to hard, and the whole rta thing will fall apart, because who are you to stop 2 mid range guilds from teaming up, and killing any rot mob they see up? You can't actually, because SOE doesn't enforce our little 'civil' game of Wait Your Turn.<br>
<br>
   I'm so sick of all the self rightious we are better than you attitudes. And I know I'm not the only one. In the end, all I can say is how dissapointed I am at how quickly this fell into name calling, and you can't do that because we said so. Then you bring up words like 'mature' and 'civilized' in your own tired defense. Be careful who you tell can play, and who has to go home. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=89179">Akaoi's Gear</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
